name: World Tour Stickman High Diving
description:
From the Sphinx to the top of the Burj Khalifa, Stickman High Diving is back and better than ever!

From the creators of Stickman Trampoline (3 million players) and Stickman High Diving (500,000+ players).

Grab your diving gear and start your journey around the globe. Cheat death as you dive from 6 world famous monuments. Impress the crowd and earn tips along the way!

FEATURES:

*Addicting gameplay: touch, jump and flip. Become a diving master!
*Stunning original artwork of the worlds most famous monuments. Unlock them all!
*Complete the objectives at each location to earn coins & unlock the next challenge.
*More locations coming soon!

Are you up for the challenge? Grab your passport and download now!

******************************

We love getting feedback from our users. Please leave us a review if you enjoy the game, and feel free to request the next features or locations!
